  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractPriorityRule<A>
    An abstract comparator that provides construction of the Comparison wrapper allowing subclasses to focus on the actual comparison of ligands.
    AtomicNumberRule<A>
    An abstract class for constitutional priority based on atomic number.

    A priority rule made up of other rules.
    DuplicateAtomRule<A>

    A simple insertion sort for ligands.
